Terabot The goal of this project was to design, development and manufacturing a prototype of a sophisticated mechanism capable of functioning in constrained and harsh terrain region using electromagnetic gripper arms. The objective of this project is not only to pick & place object but also to overcome the hurdles in its path without any difficulty.
    This involves
Working in constrained space. Elimination of suspension. Study and synthesis of combined mechanismims.
  • Material handling in industries.
  • To pick and place object on accurate location even in harsh terrain.
  • Lifting of thin metallic sheets.
  • Military surveillance.
  • Pipe and duct investigation.
  • Maintenance in nuclear power plants.
  • Bomb diffusing in bomb diffuser squad.
  • Spraying of water and pesticides in agricultural field.
